{"tid":675015,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【世盃故事】長友佑都獲臨盆妻子諒解 赴土耳其取雙贏 「生涯最美好一季」","createTime":"2018-05-23T07:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T07:57:07.000Z","uid":1121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"db1f600a136483186762c3f032561c2442da14bc","tid":675015,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:50:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180523/s00006/7055bbc0e8f6cc5d52beae846d3941e3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180523%2Fs00006%2F7055bbc0e8f6cc5d52beae846d3941e3.jpg&h=ac34bd0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本國腳長友佑都昨晚與妻兒返國，並將向國家隊報到，集訓備戰下月展開的俄羅斯世界盃，以及此前3場的熱身賽。這名31歲後衛為了前途今年1月突從國際米蘭借投土耳其球會加拉塔沙雷，未能陪伴當時快要臨盆的妻子平愛梨，早前他協助該會奪得聯賽冠軍後，亦不忘答謝對方所作出的犧牲，昨他亦不諱言這次外借決定正確，形容今季「是生涯最美好的一季」。<br />\n<br />\n在國際米蘭度過7年光景的長友佑都，今季季初因得不到新帥史巴列堤重用，漸失正選下決意季中出走，避免因狀態問題或失入選日本世界盃大軍名單的機會。結果1月他毅然選擇外借至土超的加拉塔沙雷，而當時其妻子、日本女星平愛梨適逢即將臨盆，這次決定令長友佑都有一段時間未能陪伴留在意大利產子的平愛梨身邊，對此長友佑都亦充滿感謝之情，感激對方的諒解，而如今這決定亦似乎得到「雙贏」結果，他不但如願入選「藍武士」27人集訓大軍，更在半年間穩居加拉塔沙雷正選一席，協助球會事隔3季再次贏得土超冠軍，亦是他生涯首次贏得聯賽錦標。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚用嬰兒腰帶抱住愛兒的長友，與妻子飛抵成田機場後，再次向傳媒公開感謝對方，並坦言︰「今季對我來說，是生涯最美好的一季。當時（外借）我曾擔心過，但我帶着必定要成功的覺悟，最終亦很高興一切能如願，並能為球隊作出貢獻。」據報擁有優先購買權的加軍，已打算正式買斷對方收歸旗下，料來季將續於土耳其征戰。"},{"pid":"61e60d086d3d14d30be2db4fff89d91b67c251da","tid":675015,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://contents.oricon.co.jp/upimg/news/20160925/2078919_201609250240128001474792009c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.oricon.co.jp%2Fupimg%2Fnews%2F20160925%2F2078919_201609250240128001474792009c.jpg&h=cc2919f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"282cbe7b8de042a57653bec438b973c87c586f51","tid":675015,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:52:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://auctions.c.yimg.jp/images.auctions.yahoo.co.jp/image/dr000/auc0403/users/1/6/4/2/pomponpmo-img702x1200-1520180519xalmwj26790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauctions.c.yimg.jp%2Fimages.auctions.yahoo.co.jp%2Fimage%2Fdr000%2Fauc0403%2Fusers%2F1%2F6%2F4%2F2%2Fpomponpmo-img702x1200-1520180519xalmwj26790.jpg&h=3056cda3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.fril.jp/img/96457329/m/271645718.jpg?1503433810\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.fril.jp%2Fimg%2F96457329%2Fm%2F271645718.jpg%3F1503433810&h=77d04ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://auctions.c.yimg.jp/images.auctions.yahoo.co.jp/image/dr000/auc0312/users/1/6/4/2/pomponpmo-img313x470-1513527368vuf8ug13064.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fauctions.c.yimg.jp%2Fimages.auctions.yahoo.co.jp%2Fimage%2Fdr000%2Fauc0312%2Fusers%2F1%2F6%2F4%2F2%2Fpomponpmo-img313x470-1513527368vuf8ug13064.jpg&h=c12fb68c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e72d4c1bb617f8af237b6f3303eb228c994abcc","tid":675015,"uid":54359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"同景子bb係同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2067bc5a6478157c7ac8af538df32edbe923a2","tid":675015,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:54:59.000Z","msg":"迦南<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0da0b21e697d6569a056c0100867ff797472dd","tid":675015,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:55:12.000Z","msg":"踢七年廢物米蘭冇冠軍，踢半季土超就拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"347c46370cf140777b469998a7cacad782a63c63","tid":675015,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T07:57:07.000Z","msg":"二十世紀少年"}]}